<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Masker" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Masker,</orth> one that takes part in a masquerade: <cit><quote>the --s come,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.157" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 157</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Lewis is sending over --s, to revel it with him,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.224" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 3, 224</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.1.94" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 94</bibl>. <cit><quote>a m. and a reveller,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 5.1.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. V, 1, 62</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>